---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Riya Hariyaplar | Skills & Achievements</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f8fbff;
        --bg-soft: #eef5ff;
        --card: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
        --card-border: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.18);
        --text: #122033;
        --muted: #4f6480;
        --accent: #2f6fed;
        --accent-2: #5c8df6;
        --line: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.2);
        --shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.08);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.3), transparent 30%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.45), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fbff 45%, #eef5ff 100%);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .container {
        width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 2rem));
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      nav {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 20;
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.12);
      }

      .nav-inner {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 1.1rem 0;
        gap: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .brand {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        color: #17325c;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        color: var(--muted);
        padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        transition: 0.2s ease;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover {
        background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.12);
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .nav-links a.active {
        background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.14);
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      main {
        padding: 3.5rem 0 4rem;
      }

      .page-header {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.75rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 4.4rem);
        line-height: 1.02;
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
        color: #10213a;
      }

      .page-subtitle {
        max-width: 850px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1.08rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      section {
        margin-top: 3.5rem;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        color: #17325c;
      }

      .section-line {
        height: 1px;
        width: 100%;
        background: var(--line);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .card {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        border-radius: 24px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        padding: 1.8rem;
      }

      .stats-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .stat-card {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.92), rgba(238,245,255,0.92));
        border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.14);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 1.4rem;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.06);
      }

      .stat-label {
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .stat-value {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        color: var(--accent);
      }

      .stat-note {
        margin-top: 0.7rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .soft-grid,
      .testimonial-grid,
      .cert-grid,
      .achievement-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .soft-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }

      .soft-card,
      .testimonial-card,
      .cert-card,
      .achievement-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.14);
        border-radius: 22px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.06);
        padding: 1.4rem;
      }

      .soft-card h3,
      .cert-card h3,
      .achievement-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 0.55rem 0;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: #17325c;
      }

      .soft-card p,
      .cert-card p,
      .achievement-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.8;
      }

      .soft-icon,
      .achievement-icon,
      .cert-icon {
        width: 52px;
        height: 52px;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent);
        margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
      }

      .testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .testimonial-card {
        position: relative;
      }

      .quote-mark {
        font-size: 3rem;
        line-height: 1;
        color: rgba(47, 111, 237, 0.18);
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.7rem;
        right: 1rem;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .testimonial-text {
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.9;
        margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        padding-right: 1rem;
      }

      .testimonial-name {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #17325c;
      }

      .testimonial-role {
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.96rem;
        margin-top: 0.2rem;
      }

      .skill-bars {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.15rem;
      }

      .skill-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr 64px;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      .skill-name {
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #17325c;
      }

      .bar-track {
        width: 100%;
        height: 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.12);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .bar-fill {
        height: 100%;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2f6fed, #60a5fa);
      }

      .bar-score {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-weight: 700;
        text-align: right;
      }

      .cert-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .cert-card a,
      .achievement-card a {
        color: var(--accent);
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      .achievement-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .achievement-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        margin-top: 0.9rem;
        padding: 0.45rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .speech-card {
        padding: 1.7rem;
      }

      .speech-list {
        margin: 1rem 0 0 0;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.9;
      }

      .speech-list li + li {
        margin-top: 0.45rem;
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 4rem;
        padding: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-align: center;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.12);
      }

      @media (max-width: 980px) {
        .stats-grid,
        .soft-grid,
        .testimonial-grid,
        .cert-grid,
        .achievement-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }

        .skill-row {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
          gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .bar-score {
          text-align: left;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .nav-inner {
          justify-content: center;
        }

        .brand {
          width: 100%;
          text-align: center;
        }

        .nav-links {
          justify-content: center;
        }

        .stats-grid,
        .soft-grid,
        .testimonial-grid,
        .cert-grid,
        .achievement-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav>
      <div class="container nav-inner">
        <div class="brand">Riya Hariyaplar</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">About</a>
          <a href="/resume">Resume</a>
          <a href="/skills" class="active">Skills &amp; Achievements</a>
          <a href="/interests">Interests</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Skills &amp; Achievements</h1>
        <div class="page-subtitle">
          A snapshot of the strengths, recognitions, and technical depth that shape how I work. From cross-functional collaboration and ownership to data, product, and analytical execution.
        </div>
      </div>

      <section>
        <div class="section-title">At a Glance</div>
        <div class="section-line"></div>

        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-label">Years of Experience</div>
            <div class="stat-value">4+</div>
            <div class="stat-note">Across internships, project leadership, analytics, and product-focused work.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-label">Markets Worked Across</div>
            <div class="stat-value">21</div>
            <div class="stat-note">Cross-market thinking shaped by enterprise-scale demographic and data work.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-label">Teams Collaborated With</div>
            <div class="stat-value">35+</div>
            <div class="stat-note">Experience partnering with product, engineering, analytics, marketing, and strategy teams.</div>
          </div>

          <div class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-label">Leadership / Awards</div>
            <div class="stat-value">6+</div>
            <div class="stat-note">Recognition spanning finance, academics, and competitive speech &amp; debate.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="section-title">Soft Skills</div>
        <div class="section-line"></div>

        <div class="soft-grid">
          <div class="soft-card">
            <div class="soft-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.79 2.99-4S17.66 3 16 3s-3 1.79-3 4 1.34 4 3 4Zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.79 2.99-4S9.66 3 8 3 5 4.79 5 7s1.34 4 3 4Zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V20h14v-3.5C15 14.17 10.33 13 8 13Zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.96 1.97 3.45V20h6v-3.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Cross-Functional Communication</h3>
            <p>I’m strongest when translating between technical and non-technical stakeholders, aligning teams around what matters, and keeping momentum clear across product, data, and strategy conversations.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="soft-card">
            <div class="soft-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19.14 12.94c.04-.31.06-.63.06-.94s-.02-.63-.06-.94l2.03-1.58a.5.5 0 0 0 .12-.64l-1.92-3.32a.5.5 0 0 0-.6-.22l-2.39.96a7.03 7.03 0 0 0-1.63-.94l-.36-2.54A.5.5 0 0 0 13.9 2h-3.8a.5.5 0 0 0-.49.42l-.36 2.54c-.58.22-1.12.53-1.63.94l-2.39-.96a.5.5 0 0 0-.6.22L2.71 8.48a.5.5 0 0 0 .12.64l2.03 1.58c-.04.31-.06.63-.06.94s.02.63.06.94L2.83 14.16a.5.5 0 0 0-.12.64l1.92 3.32a.5.5 0 0 0 .6.22l2.39-.96c.51.41 1.05.72 1.63.94l.36 2.54a.5.5 0 0 0 .49.42h3.8a.5.5 0 0 0 .49-.42l.36-2.54c.58-.22 1.12-.53 1.63-.94l2.39.96a.5.5 0 0 0 .6-.22l1.92-3.32a.5.5 0 0 0-.12-.64l-2.03-1.58ZM12 15.5A3.5 3.5 0 1 1 12 8a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7.5Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Ownership &amp; Initiative</h3>
            <p>I naturally look for gaps, build structure where needed, and take initiative beyond the base ask, especially in ambiguous settings where creating clarity is part of the work itself.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="soft-card">
            <div class="soft-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2 1 21h22L12 2Zm0 4.84L19.53 19H4.47L12 6.84ZM11 10v4h2v-4h-2Zm0 6v2h2v-2h-2Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Analytical Judgment</h3>
            <p>I like solving messy problems by finding the underlying signal, whether that’s through data, market context, user patterns, or a more strategic framing of the problem.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="section-title">Testimonials</div>
        <div class="section-line"></div>

        <div class="testimonial-grid">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-mark">“</div>
            <p class="testimonial-text">
              Riya consistently brought a rare combination of initiative, structure, and thoughtful problem-solving. She was able to zoom out strategically while still staying grounded in execution, and she made cross-functional collaboration feel natural.
            </p>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Anuradha Siva</div>
            <div class="testimonial-role">American Express</div>
          </div>

          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="quote-mark">“</div>
            <p class="testimonial-text">
              What stands out most about Riya is her work ethic and coachability. She’s the kind of person who takes feedback seriously, elevates the people around her, and brings real energy to every project she touches.
            </p>
            <div class="testimonial-name">Brandon Mun</div>
            <div class="testimonial-role">Colleague &amp; Mentor</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="section-title">Technical Skills Snapshot</div>
        <div class="section-line"></div>

        <div class="card">
          <div class="skill-bars">
            <div class="skill-row">
              <div class="skill-name">SQL</div>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 92%;"></div></div>
              <div class="bar-score">4.6 / 5</div>
            </div>

            <div class="skill-row">
              <div class="skill-name">Python</div>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 88%;"></div></div>
              <div class="bar-score">4.4 / 5</div>
            </div>

            <div class="skill-row">
              <div class="skill-name">Product Strategy</div>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 90%;"></div></div>
              <div class="bar-score">4.5 / 5</div>
            </div>

            <div class="skill-row">
              <div class="skill-name">Data Visualization</div>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 84%;"></div></div>
              <div class="bar-score">4.2 / 5</div>
            </div>

            <div class="skill-row">
              <div class="skill-name">Experimentation / A-B Testing</div>
              <div class="bar-track"><div class="bar-fill" style="width: 80%;"></div></div>
              <div class="bar-score">4.0 / 5</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="section-title">Certifications</div>
        <div class="section-line"></div>

        <div class="cert-grid">
          <div class="cert-card">
            <div class="cert-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19 3H5a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v14l4-3h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2Zm-8 9H7v-2h4v2Zm6-4H7V6h10v2Zm0 8H7v-2h10v2Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Excel Skills for Business</h3>
            <p>Coursera certification focused on spreadsheet modeling, data organization, practical analysis, and business-facing reporting workflows.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="cert-card">
            <div class="cert-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 3 1 9l11 6 9-4.91V17h2V9L12 3Zm0 13L5.74 12.59 12 9.17l6.26 3.42L12 16Zm-7 1.27V21h14v-3.73l-7 3.82-7-3.82Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>High-Dimensional Data Analysis</h3>
            <p>HarvardX / edX coursework focused on modern statistical learning techniques, dimensionality challenges, and advanced data analysis methods.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <div class="section-title">Achievements</div>
        <div class="section-line"></div>

        <div class="achievement-grid">
          <div class="achievement-card">
            <div class="achievement-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17 3H7v2H3v3c0 2.97 2.16 5.43 5 5.91V16H6v2h12v-2h-2v-2.09c2.84-.48 5-2.94 5-5.91V5h-4V3Zm-9 8.82A3.01 3.01 0 0 1 5 8V7h3v4.82ZM19 8a3.01 3.01 0 0 1-3 3.82V7h3v1Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Goldman Sachs Possibilities Summit Fellow</h3>
            <p>
              Selected for Goldman Sachs’ Possibilities program, a highly selective student opportunity centered on professional development, networking, and early exposure to the financial services industry.
            </p>
            <div class="achievement-badge">Finance / Early Talent Recognition</div>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.9rem;">
              <a href="https://www.goldmansachs.com/careers/students/programs-and-internships/americas/possibilities-series" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                View official program
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="achievement-card">
            <div class="achievement-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 6h16v2H4V6Zm2 4h12v2H6v-2Zm-2 4h16v2H4v-2Zm2 4h12v2H6v-2Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Bruin Hedge Fund</h3>
            <p>
              Selected into Bruin Hedge Fund, a highly competitive UCLA investing organization known for its strong finance training and selective admissions process.
            </p>
            <div class="achievement-badge">4% Acceptance Rate</div>
            <p style="margin-top: 0.9rem;">
              <a href="https://www.bruinhedgefund.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                Visit Bruin Hedge Fund
              </a>
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="achievement-card speech-card" style="grid-column: 1 / -1;">
            <div class="achievement-icon">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M3 5h18v10H7l-4 4V5Zm4 4v2h10V9H7Z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Speech &amp; Debate Recognition</h3>
            <p>
              A strong through-line in my background has been public speaking, argumentation, and communicating ideas with clarity under pressure. These achievements reflect both competitive excellence and the communication skills I bring into professional settings.
            </p>

            <ul class="speech-list">
              <li>MLK Speech &amp; Debate Tournament — Finalist</li>
              <li>SCU Cronin Dempsey Tournament — 2nd Place</li>
              <li>Stanford Speech &amp; Debate Tournament — 7th Place Winner</li>
              <li>UC Berkeley Speech &amp; Debate Tournament — Finalist</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="achievement-badge">Public Speaking • Persuasion • Executive Presence</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      2026 Riya Hariyaplar. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
